OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1776593186
OL,3,CEasyJet passengers asked to leave
OL,4,Cplane that was too heavy
OL,6,FAn easyJet plane was unable to take
OL,7,Foff until five passengers disembarked
OL,8,Fbecause it was too heavy.
OL,10,FThe airline said the incident at
OL,11,FSouthend airport, Essex on April 11
OL,12,Fhappened because safety was its
OL,13,F"highest priority".
OL,15,FOnline news outlet Your Southend
OL,16,Freported that the pilot initially
OL,17,Fannounced that the flight to Malaga,
OL,18,FSpain, would not take off unless
OL,19,Feither six passengers left the plane,
OL,20,For all the luggage was offloaded.
OL,26,@uD@AOUuD@RO]
