OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1776593186
OL,3,CEasyJet passengers asked to leave
OL,4,Cplane that was too heavy
OL,6,FThe flight eventually departed after
OL,7,Ffive people volunteered not to travel.
OL,9,FThey were provided with transport to
OL,10,FGatwick airport, from where they flew
OL,11,Fto Malaga the same day.
OL,13,FPassenger Carly Mowbray told Your
OL,14,FSouthend: "The people who got off
OL,15,Fdeparted to a round of applause from
OL,16,Fthose of us that stayed.
OL,18,F"The flight crew said they had not
OL,19,Fexperienced it before."
OL,26,@vD@KOUzD@AOU{D@WO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/6
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1776593186
OL,3,CEasyJet passengers asked to leave
OL,4,Cplane that was too heavy
OL,6,FShe added: "There were already 10
OL,7,Fempty seats before the extra
OL,8,Fpassengers got off."
OL,10,FEasyJet said in a statement: "Five
OL,11,Fpassengers on flight EJU7008 from
OL,12,FSouthend to Malaga on Saturday
OL,13,Fvolunteered to travel on alternative
OL,14,Fflights as a result of the aircraft
OL,15,Fbeing over the weight limits for the
OL,16,Fweather conditions and the short
OL,17,Flength of the runway.
OL,19,F"Weight restrictions are in place for
OL,20,Fall airlines for safety reasons.
OL,26,@nD@LOUpD@TO]rD@^OU{D@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/6
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1776593186
OL,3,CEasyJet passengers asked to leave
OL,4,Cplane that was too heavy
OL,6,F"The customers were provided with
OL,7,Ftransport and a later flight to Malaga
OL,8,Fon the same day, free of charge, from
OL,9,FLondon Gatwick and we have been in
OL,10,Ftouch with them to provide the
OL,11,Fcompensation they are entitled to, in
OL,12,Fline with regulations.
OL,14,F"The safety and welfare of our
OL,15,Fpassengers and crew is always
OL,16,FeasyJet's highest priority."
OL,18,FThe same thing happened on an easyJet
OL,19,Fflight on the same route in 2014.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOUxD@\O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/6
