OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1776593186
OL,3,CEasyJet passengers asked to leave
OL,4,Cplane that was too heavy
OL,6,FIt is up to airlines and passengers to
OL,7,Fagree compensation amounts when the
OL,8,Flatter volunteer not to travel on a
OL,9,Fbooked flight.
OL,11,FUnder UK261 rules, passengers denied
OL,12,Fboarding for a medium-haul flight such
OL,13,Fas between Southend and Malaga are
OL,14,Fentitled to #175 or #350 compensation,
OL,15,Fdepending on the length of the delay.
OL,17,FSouthend airport's 1,856-metre runway
OL,18,Fis shorter than many used by easyJet,
OL,19,Fmeaning pilots have less distance to
OL,20,Freach the required take-off speed.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/6
